_sText:
gg_Zengarden_Beta

Map Background Story:

After years of fighting on different maps you have made your way to the floating Islands of the Zengarden. But only One can continue his way to salvation. The others have to walk this arena as blue flames for all eternity.

About The Map:

  • 4 spawnpoints (2 CT / 2 T)
  • 32 playerspawns
  • particle effects
  • cubemaps
  • soundscapes
  • "real" sun

Unfortunatley I couldnt get the HUD file to work. Also there is a .nav file available, but regarding the size I didnt pack it into the map. If someone wants it, dont hesitate to PM me.

Critics / Feedback:

This is my first released map. So please dear Banana-Mappers, if you can spare a few minutes, take a look at the map. Any feedback on lighting/ gameplay / optimization etc. would be much appreciated.

Altough I used the "beta" tag, the map is staple in my opinion. But I plan to release a final version after I get feedback.

Credits:

Please see the "credits" Box on the left side. If I forgot to add someone, contact me. I will fix it right away.

Other:

Please dont decompile. If you need anything or want to know something about the map, PM me.

If anyone takes up the map for a server, PLZ let me know. I would love to play a few rounds on a live server.
